## Introduction

This chart bootstraps a {{ template "chart.name" . }} deployment on a Kubernetes cluster using the Helm package manager.

## Prerequisites

- Kubernetes 1.29.1+
- Helm 3.14.0+
- PV provisioner support in the underlying infrastructure (for charts that need persistence)

## Installing the Chart

~~~bash
# Add the repository
helm repo add k8s-charts https://kriegalex.github.io/k8s-charts/

# Install the chart
helm install my-release k8s-charts/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
~~~

> **Tip**: List all releases using `helm list`

## Uninstalling the Chart

~~~bash
helm delete my-release
~~~

