## Persistence

This chart creates a PersistentVolumeClaim to store the application data. The volume will not be deleted when you uninstall the chart. If you want to delete the PVC, you need to do it manually.

~~~bash
kubectl delete pvc -l app.kubernetes.io/instance=my-release
~~~
